TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed MsoPresetTextEffect extends System.Enum

Docs.summary: Specifies what text effect to use on a WordArt object.

remarks.para: Refer to the WordArt Gallery dialog box in any Microsoft Office product that supports WordArt to see a preview of each effect. The values of the MsoPresetTextEffect constants correspond to the formats listed in the WordArt Gallery dialog box (numbered from left to right and from top to bottom).
